QuestData.Title: Call of the Talon King
QuestData.Description:
$p, you have done much for my people. I wish to thank you on their behalf.
Please visit Veil Terokk when you can.
QuestData.PortraitGiverText: The Talon King calls you back to Veil Terokk.
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak with the Shade of Terokk in Veil Terokk.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Speak with the Shade of Terokk in Veil Terokk.
